PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>
PREFIX std: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>

SELECT ?zoneLabel ?propLabel ?endpoint ?mpcName WHERE {
  # Zones (targets)
  ?zone a std:Zone .
  ?zone rdfs:label ?zoneLabel .

  # Properties associated with each zone
  ?zone std:hasProperty ?prop .
  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .

  # Exclude writable properties
  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?prop brick:writable true }

  # Optional endpoint references for ALC and MPC
  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:endpoint ?endpoint . }
  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcName . }
}
ORDER BY ?zoneLabel ?propLabel
